        <mxCell id="parts_box" value="&lt;b&gt;Parts List&lt;/b&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align:left;font-size:10px;line-height:1.6&quot;&gt;1. 12V 60W IP67 Power Supply&lt;br&gt;2. 5V 1.8A Buck Converter (12V→5V)&lt;br&gt;3. ESP32-U (WROOM-32U) + 2.4GHz antenna&lt;br&gt;4. &lt;b&gt;4-Channel&lt;/b&gt; 5V Relay Module (opto-isolated)&lt;br&gt;5. Up to 4× 12V DC Pumps or Solenoid Valves&lt;br&gt;6. Momentary pushbutton (optional)&lt;br&gt;7. Weatherproof enclosure&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#CCCCCC;arcSize=4;fontSize=11;" vertex="1" parent="1">
